item.dc:creator: Peregrihn
item.description:
I think the saxophone entrance at 0:40 sounds a bit forced and out of place, the horn sound you used isn’t my favorite but the track is overall really cool because of where you take it and how the chords and melody evolve near the end. The abrupt end also doesn’t seem to fit to me but if you probably have a meaning behind it than I understand that’s cool
